What you need to know:  Tergat’s appointment is an apt reward for a man who is passionate about athletics — and sports in general— and continues to inspire many young runners across and beyond KenyaOnce again, with Tergat as the ambassador for this global showpiece, the world’s attention will be trained on Kenya to see how we perform in AustraliaTergat’s appointment couldn’t have come at a better time, considering we hold our national cross-country championships this Saturday at the Kenya Prisons Training College in Ruiru